ring and hence opens up an avenue towards a\nmodel-independent evaluation of the $(g-2)_\\mu$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Dec 2014 21:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-18"}
