 the same as $W_2(t)$ up to a constant.\n  The main method of this paper is the moment method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Dec 2014 00:29:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 21 Dec 2014 16:32:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 28 May 2015 19:15:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-29"}
